{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2133442, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "什么算欣赏呢", "timestamp": 1627221591, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2133525, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": 2133442, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 就是比如怎么评价好的爵士乐，好听在哪里等等", "timestamp": 1627222514, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2133665, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "猜测dz可能听不太出来即兴部分的逻辑？听多个版本的标准曲，然后需要懂一点点爵士的乐理", "timestamp": 1627224092, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2135293, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": 2133665, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 乐理大概有哪些呢？我感觉爵士各个乐器的配合度不高，听不出总体的效果。是不是听爵士同时只听一个声部，然后可以换着声部听？", "timestamp": 1627268024, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2135513, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "乐理就是爵士和弦、音阶。爵士音乐一般是乐队即兴，有标准曲，旋律走向是固定的，“总体的效果”已经规定好了。乐手表演的时候在这个基础上自由发挥。爵士乐是 合奏-各个乐器solo-合奏 的模式，不需要换声部听。", "timestamp": 1627270815, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2135564, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": 2135293, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: dz如果想评价好的爵士乐的话，爵士乐的灵魂就在即兴，一般不是讲某一首曲目好听，而是同一首曲目有很多不同的版本，“某位乐手的某一场表演中，他的即兴部分很精彩”。", "timestamp": 1627271425, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2135967, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": 2135513, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 谢谢bob说的这么详细~ 之前也有听过一两次爵士音乐会，还有那种完全即兴的，乐手在轮到自己主导的时候热情也都很高hh", "timestamp": 1627275220, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2135983, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": 2135564, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 但是我想即兴的“精彩”应该不局限于乐手的投入程度、身体语言以及和观众的反响？在音乐本身有没有什么普遍的评价标准呢？", "timestamp": 1627275329, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2136064, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": 2135983, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: dz的理解是对的，爵士乐的即兴就是dz说的“完全即兴”，精彩的评价标准就是指音乐上的，听乐手现场创作的这段旋律有没有耳目一新畅快淋漓的感觉。举一个不太恰当的例子，可以理解成只要听众还能接受的范围内，离调越厉害、不协和色彩越浓，就越精彩", "timestamp": 1627275977, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2136101, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": 2135983, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 所以得先听jazz standard（最早的版本，一般是上世纪30到50年代的)然后再听各个乐手即兴出来的“面目全非”的样子。", "timestamp": 1627276323, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2140450, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": 2136101, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob:有点意思哈哈，bob能不能留个微信以后多加交流呢", "timestamp": 1627312313, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2140464, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": 2136101, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 推荐一些曲目什么的", "timestamp": 1627312373, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2140542, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": 2140464, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 就不微信上洞了hhh可以直接搜jazz standard的歌单", "timestamp": 1627312798, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2141543, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": 2140542, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 没事没事", "timestamp": 1627318640, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2150632, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": 2140542, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: bob有点像我认识的一个同学哈哈，能冒昧问一下性别吗", "timestamp": 1627440297, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2150721, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 413775, "reply_to": 2150632, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: ♂嘿嘿", "timestamp": 1627441020, "ty